\cf0 \cb2 Andrew Lazar - Barclays Bank PLC, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Megan Christine Alexander - Morgan Stanley, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Peter Galbo - BofA Securities, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Peter Grom - UBS Investment Bank, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 David Palmer - Evercore ISI Institutional Equities, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Leah Jordan - Goldman Sachs Group, Inc., Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Max Andrew Gumport - BNP Paribas, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 James Salera - Stephens Inc., Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Thomas Palmer - JPMorgan Chase & Co, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Michael Lavery - Piper Sandler & Co., Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Alexia Howard - Bernstein Institutional Services LLC, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Matthew Smith - Stifel, Nicolaus & Company, Incorporated, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Robert Moskow - TD Cowen, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Scott Marks - Jefferies LLC, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Christopher Carey - Wells Fargo Securities, LLC, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 John Baumgartner - Mizuho Securities USA LLC, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Bingqing Zhu - Rothschild & Co Redburn, Research Division\cb1 \
